# Sidecar binaries are produced per-platform by CI / the publish profile
# (see tauri.conf.json -> bundle.externalBin "binaries/koine"). Tauri resolves
# them with a target-triple suffix (e.g. koine-aarch64-apple-darwin). They are
# build artifacts, not source — never commit them. A local placeholder may exist
# here to satisfy the build-script validation during development.
koine-*
